        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫人叫奴把花采，\n急急忙忙就出堂来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家，文艳，洛阳人氏。兄长刘二，只因家中遭了人命，我兄妹二人逃出在外，\n投在这相府，把奴做了一个侍女丫鬟。到此已有数月之久，幸蒙夫人待奴恩\n宽，只是常常做此使女，何日是个出头之日。我想老爷，膝下无子，若能与他\n成却了这等一桩好事，奴岂不是一位偏房夫人。怎奈无有机会勾引于他，也是\n枉然。咳，只好慢慢等候便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有文艳我这里暗自思忖，\n为使女何日里才是出身。\n那时节奴就是偏房夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此花园，夫人叫我采花，不免前去。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春光明媚艳阳天，万紫千红满花园。莫道腊梅开得晚，此花专能耐冬寒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张尚书内咳。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看那边来了一人，好像我家老爷模样，不免我藏在太湖石边，等他到来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张尚书上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有老夫下朝来无可消遣，\n信步儿来在了自己花园。\n又只见小文艳手提花篮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "转过了回廊用目看、刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍儿与老爷叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢老爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文艳，你不在上房侍奉夫人，到此为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷非知，侍儿奉了夫人之命，叫奴到此花园采花玩赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然夫人叫你采花。你就采花去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在花园领了老爷谕，\n转面来向前去攀取花枝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一朵开得好。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘文艳摘。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一朵也到好。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘文艳摘。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "各样的花朵摘采遍，\n看看不觉摆满篮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文艳，你手中摘的是什么花？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍儿这手中么，乃是一朵芙蓉花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此花有何好处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此花甚有好处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有什么好处，你且讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷容禀："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此花生在太液旁，道它如面艳无双。芙蓉做就消魂帐，良宵同枕宿鸳鸯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上两句还好，下两句不佳。上房去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里用言语对他讲，\n他佯佯不睬为哪桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘文艳走俏步两边看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好叫我春心动难以主张。\n管叫他与奴家成却鸾凰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我只得假意儿再把话讲、张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文艳，你为何去而复转？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是侍儿去而复转，只是花中之意未曾讲完。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想这园中四季之花，开连不断，红红绿绿，有香有色。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "牡丹占尽艳阳春，桃李无言意更深。葛花满把能消酒，栀子同心好赠人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听你之言莫非你有什么心事不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍儿心事倒有，只是在老爷面前，不好开言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有什么心事，只管的说来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想老爷身居宰相，并无有三房四妾。侍儿文艳，不才情愿与老爷铺床叠被，侍\n奉老爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好贱人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "贱人说话太张狂，\n不由老夫怒胸膛。\n怎能与贱婢配成双。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大文艳，不顾羞耻，竟敢出此狂言。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贱人说话没来由，倒叫老夫怒心头。凤凰怎与乌鸦配，水性杨花最下流。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个不知羞耻的贱人！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张尚书下。刘文艳跪，偷看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，奴与他好言相对，他一怒而去，反把我羞辱一场。不免我去至上房，回见\n夫人便了。哎呀且住！想我家老爷回至上房，见了夫人提起了此事，那时府中\n内外之人倘若知道此事，叫奴家是怎样为人，是如何的为人？哦喝有了！我不\n免将衣衫扯破，粉脸抓破。我家夫人乃是一位贤德之人，倘若是将计就计，将\n我与老爷婚配，做一个二房，也未可知。我就此装扮起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实指望与老爷成就姻眷，\n又谁知他那里把我羞惭。\n故意儿撕罗裙扯破衣衫。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘文艳卸簪环。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有文艳用妙计巧来装扮，\n到上房见夫人细说根源。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘文艳走浪头三次，下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "刘文艳→张尚书",
