    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "丫鬟",
        "丫鬟引路二堂上",
        "倒不如将衣衫来脱下",
        "刘二",
        "刘文艳",
        "家院",
        "张夫人",
        "张小姐",
        "张尚书",
        "走向前来双膝跪",
        "转回头望夫人将奴来放",
        "院子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张夫人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老爷当朝为首相，\n一家大小受荣光。\n国泰民安永安康。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟引张小姐同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张小姐",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "适才梳洗出绣房，\n轻移莲步看高堂。\n尊声母亲可安康？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟引路二堂上、张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿免礼。一旁坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今晨我命文艳去到后园采花，为何这般时候，还不见到来？\n丫鬟，你去至花园，看那丫头，在那里做甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文艳来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘文艳上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "扯破衣裳抓破脸，\n假意儿含怒气珠泪涟涟。\n望求夫人把奴怜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "走向前来双膝跪、张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文艳，我命你后园采花，为何这般的光景？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人有所不知，侍儿到花园采花，遇见一人，要与奴如此如此。是侍儿不允，\n竟被那人将奴粉脸抓破，衣裳扯碎。因此侍儿速速跑回，望求夫人作主呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，你就该将那人拉来见我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是侍儿不敢拉他前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他是何人？你怎么不敢拉他前来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是旁人，就是我家的老爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大胆文艳！想我家爹爹身为宰相，位列三台，焉能作为出这无耻之事。此乃是\n你一派胡言。\n丫鬟，看家法伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张小姐",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "文艳说话太欺人，\n竟敢在此乱胡云。\n岂能要你下贱人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张夫人拦。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫声我儿且消停。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿不必生气，回转绣房去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿遵命。\n文艳过来。从今以后，不许你进我的绣房，若要进我的绣房，定要将你两腿打\n断。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "送小姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张小姐下。丫鬟羞文艳，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见小姐怒气回绣房，\n小丫鬟羞得我惭愧难当。\n我只得出门去投奔他方。"
        },
        {
          "character": "转回头望夫人将奴来放、张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看我家老爷既然做出此事，倒不如将计就计，就将文艳打扮起来，藏在房中。\n待等老爷回来，就叫他二人成了姻缘。\n啊，文艳，我将你打扮起来，你就做为老爷的二房，你看如何呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，此事使不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使得的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟，将上好的衣服拿出几件，与文艳穿了，带她到后房，梳洗打扮起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，这事断断使不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使得的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人说使得，就是使得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使得的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使得的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使得，你就与我更衣来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟扶刘文艳同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伺候夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这府门之内，将红灯挂起，红毡铺地，悬灯结彩。你家老爷不问便罢，他若问\n时，你就说是夫人我吩咐的。要记下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看看文艳打扮梳洗好了没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文艳梳洗打扮好了没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟扶刘文艳同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文艳与夫人叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看文艳打扮起来，倒像一夫人的样儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫人不必来夸奖，\n好叫文艳愧难当。\n逃出府门奔他乡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "倒不如将衣衫来脱下、张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不必羞惭。\n丫鬟，搀她到后房去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看此事断断使不得。还是脱了衣衫，我逃出府门去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人说是此事使得，就是使得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使得的？如此你就搀扶了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘文艳、丫鬟同下。张尚书上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将身来在上房里，\n见了夫人问端的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷来了。请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，这府内悬灯结彩，却是为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷非知，是妾身与老爷收了一个二房，所以张灯结彩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，想老夫若大年纪，还收得什么二房，此事断断不可。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷说哪里话来。想这官宦人家谁无有个三房四妾，你今姬妾全无，有那不知\n道者，不说你不愿纳妾，反道我不贤了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，我就允下。但不知是谁家的女儿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人么，就是你所爱之人。是你心上那个人儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我心上的人？我心上的，是哪一个呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你一见便知明白。\n丫鬟，掌灯，送你家老爷入新房。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "新人在哪里？待我看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟扶刘文艳同上，张尚书打刘文艳。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好贱人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见贱人怒气发，\n气得老夫手脚麻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷你这是为何呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人是你不知，只因今早起来，老夫在花园闲游，见这贱人在花园采花。不想\n这贱人胡言乱道，就要与老夫成亲，那时老夫一时火起，将她痛骂了一场，不\n想这贱人反在你面前，搬动是非。你道恼是不恼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她倒说是你，在花园调戏于她来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是她？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张尚书气。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "似这等无耻淫贱之人，要她何用？夫人你与我把她快快赶出府去。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恼恨贱人太痴心，搬动是非为何情？似你这等淫贱女，岂容败坏我门庭！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张尚书",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，你与我赶、赶、赶了出去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张尚书下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "院子，将她兄长刘二唤来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘二走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘二上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘二",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听夫人唤，定是赏我钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叩见夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你妹子不安本分，在府中做此不良之事，这府中不能留你二人。现有白银五两，\n你兄妹投奔他乡去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张夫人下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是哪里说起。你我兄妹二人，无依无靠，好容易有了这个吃饱饭的所在。你\n又胡思乱想，做出这等事来。被人家将我二人赶出府来，你我怎生得了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄长息怒，虽是妹子不好，但是事已如此，埋怨妹子也是无益的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天到这般时候，我二到哪里去安身？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘文艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去到前面，寻一庵观寺院，暂住一霄，待等明天，再做道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "事到如今，也只好如此。走吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。刘文艳、刘二同下。）"
        }
      ],
